<% content_for :title, "Community Guidelines - Dealo" %>
<div class="static-page">
  <div class="container static-page-container">
    <h1 class="static-page-title">Community Guidelines</h1>
    <div class="static-page-content">
      <p class="static-lead">These guidelines help keep Dealo safe and fair for everyone. By using the site you agree to follow them.</p>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Allowed content</h2>
        <ul class="static-list">
          <li>Genuine ads for items or services you are selling or offering</li>
          <li>Accurate descriptions and real photos of what you’re selling</li>
          <li>Respectful communication with other users</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Prohibited content and behaviour</h2>
        <ul class="static-list">
          <li>Illegal items or services</li>
          <li>Fraud, scams, or misleading listings</li>
          <li>Offensive, hateful, or harassing content or messages</li>
          <li>Spam, duplicate ads, or unrelated commercial promotion</li>
          <li>Impersonation of other people or brands</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Enforcement</h2>
        <p>We may remove listings, warn users, or suspend or ban accounts that break these guidelines. Serious or repeated breaches can lead to permanent removal.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="static-section">
        <h2>Reporting</h2>
        <p>If you see content or behaviour that breaks these guidelines, please <%= link_to "contact us", contact_path, class: "static-link" %> and we’ll look into it.</p>
      </section>

      <p>For staying safe when meeting in person, see our <%= link_to "Safety Tips", safety_tips_path, class: "static-link" %>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
